===============================================================================

PuckEngine has been installed successfully!

Next steps:

1. Run migrations:
   rails db:migrate

2. Mount the engine in config/routes.rb:
   mount PuckEngine::Engine => "/puck"

3. Visit the editor at:
   /puck/editor

4. Create your first page and start building!

For more information, see the README at:
https://github.com/puckeditor/puck-engine

